Class ProcessAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • soffico.customerapi.process.ProcessAdapter

    • Method Detail

      • obtainProcessIdentifier

        public static java.lang.String obtainProcessIdentifier()
        This method returns the process identifier of the process instance that is responsible for scheduling the current orchestra activity. If this method is called without any "process"-context, null is returned.
        Returns:
        The process identifier or null if no process context is available

      • obtainTokenIdentifier

        public static java.lang.String obtainTokenIdentifier()
        This method returns the token reference of the process token that is responsible for scheduling the current orchestra activity. If this method is called without any "process"-context, null is returned.
        Returns:
        The token reference or null if no process context is available

      • obtainGlobalSessionIdentifier

        public static java.lang.String obtainGlobalSessionIdentifier()
        Return a global session identifier. This method returns the process identifier of the process instance that is responsible for scheduling the current orchestra activity. If this method is called without any "process"-context, null is returned.
        Returns:
        Global session identifier or null if no process context is available
